Ukraine Willing to Pay for Russian Gas in Rubles, Interfax Says

-- B y   D a r y n a   K r a s n o l u t s k a
-- 
2011-04-21T12:46:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-21/ukraine-willing-to-pay-for-russian-gas-in-rubles-interfax-says.html
Ukraine is prepared to pay OAO
Gazprom in Russian rubles for natural gas if its eastern
neighbor agrees to review prices, Interfax reported, citing
President  Viktor Yanukovych .  The countries are currently in talks, Yanukovych said in
Cherkasy, central Ukraine, according to Interfax.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Daryna Krasnolutska in Kiev at 
 dkrasnolutsk@bloomberg.net ;  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Balazs Penz at 
 bpenz@bloomberg.net ; 